---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Natural Stone Countertops — Travertine, Limestone, Slate & Onyx
description: Travertine, limestone, slate, and onyx for counters, floors, and features — fabricated and installed across the Philadelphia suburbs, from Bucks County to Chester County.
permalink: /countertops/natural-stone/
breadcrumbs:
  - title: The Stone Library
    url: /countertops/
---

<div class="page-head page-head--split">
  <div>
    <span class="kicker"><a href="/countertops/" style="text-decoration:none">Countertops</a> · Natural Stone</span>
    <h1>{{ materialPages.naturalStone.heading }}</h1>
  </div>
  <p class="lede lede--sm" style="max-width:44ch">{{ materialPages.naturalStone.lede }}</p>
</div>

<div class="grid grid--2" style="padding:8px var(--pad-x) 56px; gap:40px">
  {% for s in materialPages.naturalStone.stones %}
    <div class="value">
      <h3>{% if s.url %}<a href="{{ s.url }}" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit">{{ s.name }}</a>{% else %}{{ s.name }}{% endif %}</h3>
      <p>{{ s.desc }}</p>
      {% if s.url %}<p style="margin-top:10px"><a class="text-link" href="{{ s.url }}">Care &amp; installation →</a></p>{% endif %}
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

{% set cta = materialPages.naturalStone.cta %}
{% include "partials/cross-cta.njk" %}
